lead_paragraph: There was a hole-in-one and an albatross two on a par-5 hole at the Nedbank Golf Challenge in South Africa on Friday, while Alex Noren collected five birdies over the back nine holes to take a 2-shot lead at the halfway mark.

headline.print_headline: Noren Ahead in South Africa, Stenson Falls 7 Shots Off Lead
